<abstract><t>In-situ Operations, Administration, and Maintenance (IOAM) records operational and telemetry information in the packet while the packet traverses a path between two points in the network.  This document outlines how encapsulations using an EtherType to identify IOAM data fields as the next header in a packet.</t></abstract>

